<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WassitDZ Game | المتجر الرسمي</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.rtl.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --primary: <%= settings.themeColor %>; }
        body { background: #f4f7f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; padding-top: 45px; }
        .announcement-bar { background: #0f172a; color: #fff; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 2000; overflow: hidden; }
        .navbar { background: #fff; height: 160px; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .logo-img { max-height: 130px; }
        .account-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); position: relative; height: 100%; border: none; }
        .sold-overlay { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index: 10; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .img-container { width: 100%; height: 200px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
        .img-container img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .acc-id { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); color: #fff; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
        .price-dz { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #10b981; }
        .btn-buy { background: #000; color: #fff; width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; padding: 8px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; display: block; text-align: center; }
        footer { background: #0f172a; color: #fff; padding: 25px 0; margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="announcement-bar" dir="rtl">
    <marquee direction="right" scrollamount="6">
        <span style="display:inline-block; padding-left: 50px;">⚡ <%= settings.announcement %> ⚡</span>
    </marquee>
</div>

<nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/"><img src="<%= settings.logoUrl %>" class="logo-img"></a>
</nav>

<div class="container mt-3 text-center">
    <a href="<%= settings.mediationLink %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary m-1">الوساطة</a>
    <a href="<%= settings.sellAccountLink %>" class="btn btn-outline-success m-1">بيع حسابك</a>
    <a href="<%= settings.supportLink %>" class="btn btn-outline-secondary m-1">الدعم الفني</a>
</div>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row g-3">
        <% accounts.forEach(acc => { %>
        <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
            <div class="account-card">
                <% if(acc.status === 'تم البيع') { %>
                    <div class="sold-overlay"><span class="badge bg-danger fs-6" style="transform: rotate(-15deg);">تم البيع</span></div>
                <% } %>
                <a href="/account/<%= acc.id %>" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <div class="img-container">
                        <span class="acc-id">#<%= acc.id %></span>
                        <img src="<%= acc.imgs[0] %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-3 text-center">
                        <span class="badge bg-light text-dark mb-1"><%= acc.linkType %></span>
                        <h6 class="fw-bold text-truncate"><%= acc.title %></h6>
                        <div class="price-dz"><%= acc.priceDZ %> د.ج</div>
                        <div class="text-muted small mb-2"><%= acc.priceUSD %> $</div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <div class="px-3 pb-3">
                    <% if(acc.status === 'متاح') { %>
                        <a href="<%= settings.buyNowLink %>" class="btn-buy">شراء الآن</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary w-100 border-0" disabled>غير متوفر</button>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-top">
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-center mb-4">آراء زبائن WassitDZ</h4>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-2">"تعامل راقي جداً وسرعة في تسليم الحساب، أنصح الجميع بالتعامل معهم."</p>
                    <div class="fw-bold small">- أيوب بن علي</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-2">"أفضل وسيط في الجزائر، ثقة وأمان 100%."</p>
                    <div class="fw-bold small">- كريم سطيف</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <p class="small text-muted mb-2">"شكراً جزيلاً، حساب رائع وبسعر ممتاز."</p>
                    <div class="fw-bold small">- محمد وهران</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5 pt-4 border-top">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-center">الأسئلة الشائعة</h4>
        <div class="accordion shadow-sm" id="faqAcc">
            <% faqs.forEach((faq, i) => { %>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed py-2" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#f<%=i%>"><%= faq.question %></button></h2>
                <div id="f<%=i%>" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAcc"><div class="accordion-body small"><%= faq.answer %></div></div>
            </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer><p class="mb-0 small">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> WassitDZ Game - جميع الحقوق محفوظة</p></footer>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
